mb|1S|mb|P|mb|2N|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Whenever partner opens a major and you have 4-card support, you must show it right away. Failure to do so denies 4 card support. That even applies if you have an outside 6-card suit. 2NT shows a game forcing hand with 4+ spades (usually 4).|
