mb|P?|nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Responders, West here, normally responds in one of the following ways. If they bid a suit at the 3-level, that shows a singleton or void in that suit.|
